{
  "stem": "21437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, during the week, we had our meals sometimes the children with the nanny or with the lady that helped us in the house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or we had somebody that was coming to clean the house, or you know, people that I think was important for my mother for us to see that they are people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just happened to be in a situation where they had to earn their living this way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Friday night, we were sitting around a table always, all of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we always had somebody from out of town who was a visitor to this town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had very often a widow, a lady that didn't have anyone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think her name was Sonja.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the second name, I don't really-- and so it was conducted with great detail and with reverence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, we just loved it, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whatever happened during the week, if we happened to have-- because the breakfast we had together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the dinners, if we happen to have together or for whatever reason we had to go-- my father had a business conference or whatever, but Friday night and Saturday lunch we always-- and dinner, as a matter of fact, whatever-- we always.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because on Sunday, the business was open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Friday night and Shabbat was closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gefilte fish, chicken soup, anything think you describe, we ate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not really so keen to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not very food lovers, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we needed to be coaxed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think this is where I sort of believe I developed, we developed a love for sitting around the table.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
